@gunan @yifeif Thank you for making this change! This is great!
From the latest run, it seems only `//py_test_dir/tensorflow/python/debug:examples_test` is failing. And it turns out to be a shell test!
So, adding `--test_lang_filters=py` as a test option should solve this problem.
